descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the enjoyable and fascinating world of Farm Blast.

Farm Blast is an amazing puzzle game for all of you who are looking for a fun way to relax the brain and pass time. Show off your strategy skills; tap and blast bubbles to solve the puzzles and create your own farm by completing levels. Solving puzzles has never been this much fun.

This endless fun tapping game is easy to play, but it is really challenging to master. You need to blast groups of bubbles that are the same color with a simple tap but with limited moves in every level, it’s all up to your smart blasts and combine the boosters for giant explosions. Try to clear the board with fewer moves to get a higher score.

Solve all the puzzles, clear all the levels, reach the target, and win cool boosters.

Rockets, bombs, and color wheels will help you smash the blocks and pass more easily in levels. Use these amazing boosts and power-ups at the right time to blast bubbles, clear the board, collect stars and win awesome prizes! Simple gameplay but hard to master.

Farm Blast is free and exciting puzzle game that will connect you for a long time! Join the color blasting adventure of Farm Blast, we are looking forward to you to challenge!

So, what are you waiting for?

Farm Blast is an amazing puzzle game for all of you who are looking for a fun way to relax the brain and pass time. Show off your strategy skills; tap and blast bubbles to solve the puzzles and create your farm by completing levels. Solving puzzles has never been this much fun.

This endless fun tapping game is easy to play, but it is challenging to master. You need to blast groups of bubbles that are the same color with a simple tap but with limited moves in every level, it’s all up to your smart blasts and combines the boosters for giant explosions. Try to clear the board with fewer moves to get a higher score.

Solve all the puzzles, clear all the levels, reach the target, and win cool boosters.

Rockets, bombs, and disco balls will help you smash the blocks and pass more easily in levels. Use these amazing boosters and power-ups at the right time to blast bubbles, clear the board, collect stars, and win awesome prizes! Simple gameplay but hard to master.

Moreover; ‘Weekly Event’ is here. You have the chance to join the various events and get a chance to win more!

Facebook Login is also available! You can continue without losing your progress on any device by logging into your account.

Farm Blast is a free and exciting puzzle game that will connect you for a long time! Join the color blasting adventure of Farm Blast, we are looking forward to you to challenge!

So, what are you waiting for?

Farm Blast is a great puzzle game for those who are looking for an entertaining way to relax their brain and pass the time. Show off your strategic skills; tap and blast the bubbles to solve the puzzles, and build up your farm by completing the levels. Solving puzzles has never been so much fun.

This game is easy to play, but challenging to master. You have to pop groups of bubbles of the same color by simply tapping on them. Since you only have a limited number of moves in each level, it depends on your clever blasts and combination of boosters for huge explosions. Try to clear the board with fewer moves to achieve a higher score.

Solve all the puzzles, clear all the levels, reach the target, and win cool boosters.

Rockets, bombs and disco balls will help you smash the blocks and pass the levels easier. Use these great boosters and power-ups at the right time to destroy bubbles, clear the board, collect stars and win great prizes! Simple gameplay, but hard to master.

There are also 'Daily Events'. You have the opportunity to participate in the various events and win even more.

Facebook login is also available. You can continue playing on any device without losing your progress by logging into your account.

Farm Blast is a free and exciting puzzle game that will keep you hooked for a long time. Get involved in the colorful adventure of Farm Blast; we look forward to your challenge!

So, what are you waiting for?

creator: Narcade
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the fascinating world of Farm Blast.

Farm Blast is a great puzzle game for those who are looking for an entertaining way to relax their brain and pass the time. Show off your strategic skills; tap and blast the bubbles to solve the puzzles, and build up your farm by completing the levels. Solving puzzles has never been so much fun.

This game is easy to play, but challenging to master. You have to pop groups of bubbles of the same color by simply tapping on them. Since you only have a limited number of moves in each level, it depends on your clever blasts and combination of boosters for huge explosions. Try to clear the board with fewer moves to achieve a higher score.

Solve all the puzzles, clear all the levels, reach the target, and win cool boosters.

Rockets, bombs and disco balls will help you smash the blocks and pass the levels easier. Use these great boosters and power-ups at the right time to destroy bubbles, clear the board, collect stars and win great prizes! Simple gameplay, but hard to master.

There are also 'Daily Events'. You have the opportunity to participate in the various events and win even more.

Facebook login is also available. You can continue playing on any device without losing your progress by logging into your account.

Farm Blast is a free and exciting puzzle game that will keep you hooked for a long time. Get involved in the colorful adventure of Farm Blast; we look forward to your challenge!

So, what are you waiting for?
descriptionShort: Solving puzzles has never been this much fun!

This game is easy to play, but challenging to master. You have to pop groups of bubbles of the same color by simply tapping on them. Since you only have a limited number of moves in each level, it depends on your clever blasts and combination of boosters for huge explosions. Try to clear the board with fewer moves to achieve a higher score.

Solve all the puzzles, clear all the levels, reach the target, and win cool boosters.

Rockets, bombs and disco balls will help you smash the blocks and pass the levels easier. Use these great boosters and power-ups at the right time to destroy bubbles, clear the board, collect stars and win great prizes! Simple gameplay, but hard to master.

There are also 'Daily Events'. You have the opportunity to participate in the various events and win even more.

Facebook login is also available. You can continue playing on any device without losing your progress by logging into your account.

Farm Blast is a free and exciting puzzle game that will keep you hooked for a long time. Get involved in the colorful adventure of Farm Blast; we look forward to your challenge!

So, what are you waiting for?
